    "body": "## Purpose\nAs part of the effort to reduce env variables (#25700), this PR introduces `AttentionConfig` and the `--attention-config` CLI argument group. The following environment variables are converted to CLI arguments:\n\n```\nVLLM_ATTENTION_BACKEND                        -> --attention-config.backend\nVLLM_FLASH_ATTN_VERSION                       -> --attention-config.flash_attn_version\nVLLM_V1_USE_PREFILL_DECODE_ATTENTION          -> --attention-config.use_prefill_decode_attention\nVLLM_FLASH_ATTN_MAX_NUM_SPLITS_FOR_CUDA_GRAPH -> --attention-config.flash_attn_max_num_splits_for_cuda_graph\nVLLM_USE_CUDNN_PREFILL                        -> --attention-config.use_cudnn_prefill\nVLLM_USE_TRTLLM_RAGGED_DEEPSEEK_PREFILL       -> --attention-config.use_trtllm_ragged_deepseek_prefill\nVLLM_USE_TRTLLM_ATTENTION                     -> --attention-config.use_trtllm_attention\nVLLM_DISABLE_FLASHINFER_PREFILL               -> --attention-config.disable_flashinfer_prefill\nVLLM_FLASHINFER_DISABLE_Q_QUANTIZATION        -> --attention-config.disable_flashinfer_q_quantization\n```\nDue to its significance, the attention backend may also be specified by `--attention-backend`\n\nBackwards compatibility is maintained with warnings for removal in v0.14.\n\nMany of the examples and tests will need to be updated. This will be done in follow-ups.\n\n## Test Plan\nCI should suffice\n\n## Test Result\n\n---\n<details>\n<summary> Essential Elements of an Effective PR Description Checklist </summary>\n\n- [x] The purpose of the PR, such as \"Fix some issue (link existing issues this PR will resolve)\".\n- [x] The test plan, such as providing test command.\n- [ ] The test results, such as pasting the results comparison before and after, or e2e results\n- [ ] (Optional) The necessary documentation update, such as updating `supported_models.md` and `examples` for a new model.\n- [ ] (Optional) Release notes update. If your change is user facing, please update the release notes draft in the [Google Doc](https://docs.google.com/document/d/1YyVqrgX4gHTtrstbq8oWUImOyPCKSGnJ7xtTpmXzlRs/edit?tab=t.0).\n</details>\n\n",
